In [53]:
for year in list_of_years:
    
   
    fig = shape.plot(column=year, cmap='tab20c', figsize=(10,10), linewidth=0.8, edgecolor='0.8', vmin=vmin, vmax=vmax,
legend=True, norm=plt.Normalize(vmin=vmin, vmax=vmax))
    
    
    fig.axis('off')
    
   
    fig.set_title('CO2 emissions in UK from 2009 to 2019', \
              fontdict={'fontsize': '25',
                         'fontweight' : '3'})
    
    
    filepath = os.path.join(output_path,only_year+'_emissions.jpg')
    chart = fig.get_figure()
    chart.savefig(filepath, dpi=400)
